name: Wsc
body:
### WebSocket Chat client
**wsc** is a jQuery plugin that provides an HTML5/CSS3 chat client for 'dAmn-like' chat servers. To get wsc, use the following commands.

```
$ git clone git://github.com/photofroggy/wsc.git
$ cd wsc
```
